---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Maxim - Angebote (Archiv)" navMode="service">
  <div class="layout">

    <a href="/" class="block border dark:border-yellow-700 border-yellow-400 bg-yellow-50 dark:bg-yellow-900 hover:bg-yellow-100 dark:hover:bg-yellow-900 rounded-xl p-4 mb-10 text-sm transition-colors duration-200">
      <p class="font-mono text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-500 text-xs">
        ⚠️ Dieser Service wird aktuell nicht mehr angeboten. Kehre hier zurück →
      </p>
      <p class="font-mono text-yellow-600 dark:text-yellow-500 text-xs">
        ⚠️ This service is currently no longer offered. Return here →
      </p>
    </a>

    <h1 id="dynamic-text6" class="transition-transform duration-300 transform hover:scale-105"></h1>

    <p>
      Du hast ein technisches Problem, dein PC läuft nicht rund oder du willst dein System aufrüsten?
      Ich helfe dir persönlich, schnell und zuverlässig – egal ob Windows, Linux oder Mac.
      <br /><br />
      <span class="block mx-auto text-center font-semibold text-indigo-400 text-xl">
        Alle Leistungen zum Festpreis von 20 €/Stunde.
      </span>
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-left mt-10">
      <div class="border-2 dark:border-dark border-light p-6 rounded-xl dark:bg-halfdark bg-light dark:text-light text-dark hover:scale-[1.03] transition-all">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold flex items-center gap-2">🔧 <span>Reparatur & Wartung</span></h3>
      </div>
      <div class="border-2 dark:border-dark border-light p-6 rounded-xl dark:bg-halfdark bg-light dark:text-light text-dark hover:scale-[1.03] transition-all">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold flex items-center gap-2">💻 <span>Windows / macOS / Linux Einrichtung</span></h3>
      </div>
      <div class="border-2 dark:border-dark border-light p-6 rounded-xl dark:bg-halfdark bg-light dark:text-light text-dark hover:scale-[1.03] transition-all">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold flex items-center gap-2">🛡️ <span>Virenentfernung & Systembereinigung</span></h3>
      </div>
      <div class="border-2 dark:border-dark border-light p-6 rounded-xl dark:bg-halfdark bg-light dark:text-light text-dark hover:scale-[1.03] transition-all">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold flex items-center gap-2">💾 <span>Datensicherung & Datenrettung</span></h3>
      </div>
      <div class="border-2 dark:border-dark border-light p-6 rounded-xl dark:bg-halfdark bg-light dark:text-light text-dark hover:scale-[1.03] transition-all">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold flex items-center gap-2">⚙️ <span>Hardware-Aufrüstung & Umbau</span></h3>
      </div>
      <div class="border-2 dark:border-dark border-light p-6 rounded-xl dark:bg-halfdark bg-light dark:text-light text-dark hover:scale-[1.03] transition-all">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold flex items-center gap-2">🧰 <span>Systemzusammenstellung</span></h3>
      </div>
      <div class="border-2 dark:border-dark border-light p-6 rounded-xl dark:bg-halfdark bg-light dark:text-light text-dark hover:scale-[1.03] transition-all">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold flex items-center gap-2">🧠 <span>Persönliche PC-Beratung</span></h3>
      </div>
      <div class="border-2 dark:border-dark border-light p-6 rounded-xl dark:bg-halfdark bg-light dark:text-light text-dark hover:scale-[1.03] transition-all">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold flex items-center gap-2">🌍 <span>Fernwartung & Online-Hilfe</span></h3>
      </div>
      <div class="border-2 dark:border-dark border-light p-6 rounded-xl dark:bg-halfdark bg-light dark:text-light text-dark hover:scale-[1.03] transition-all">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold flex items-center gap-2">📦 <span>Einrichtung neuer Geräte</span></h3>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script src="../../js/pageHandler.js"></script>
    <script src="../../js/themeHandler.js"></script>
  </div>
</Layout>